title: The Big Suey: Without Order, There Is Chaos
description:
A sparse crowd for The KFC Bucket makes us ponder sabotaging our colleagues, we bring back the polls review with an exciting new sponsor, and Ricky Williams joins to tell us about the concussions he can remember.
